rows.label: tlk42350122_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I used to live in a town called Echell,
you know!

rows.label: tlk42350122_03_msg0002
rows.name:
I fell head over heels in love with
this girl who lived there.

rows.label: tlk42350122_03_msg0003
rows.name:
She was the daughter of the lord who
ran the place. She was such a sweet,
elegant young lady!

rows.label: tlk42350122_03_msg0004
rows.name:
If I weren't a Phonex, I would
have proposed to her for sure.

rows.label: tlk42350122_03_msg0005
rows.name:
But it's weird...it seems like she
just disappeared at some point.
The whole mansion is gone now!

rows.label: tlk42350122_03_msg0006
rows.name:
It was such a shock when I found out.
I hope I see her again someday!
